    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The target of this spell appears to be about 2 feet away from its true location. The creature benefits from a 50% miss chance as if it had total concealment. Unlike actual total concealment, <em>displacement</em> doesn\u2019t prevent enemies from targeting the creature normally. True seeing reveals the target\u2019s true location and negates the miss chance. If a creature with blindsense can also see the displaced creature, the visual and blindsense information combined are enough for the creature with blindsense to attack the displaced creature without a miss chance, unlike normal for blindsense.&nbsp;</span></p>"
